data.description: Charming 3-bed, 2-bath home located on River Road in Hamilton is ready for you! This cozy ranch offers new flooring, fresh paint, and a warm, welcoming atmosphere. This property features 2 bedrooms on the main level and one additional bedroom in the lower level. The semi-finished lower level includes an additional bedroom and bathroom. Conveniently located, this home is an ideal blend of comfort and practicality, perfect for creating lasting memories.
